, said, \u201cThe virtue of knowledge is more beloved to me than the virtue of worship, and the best of your religion is conscientious piety.\u201d Source: al-A\u0304da\u0304b lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 818 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42296,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/10\/18\/knowledge-better-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":35027,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Learning better than voluntary worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 18, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of knowledge is better than the virtue of worship, and the best of your religion is conscientious piety.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 3960 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24160,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/14\/qasim-deen-salat-tazkiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35027,"position":2},"title":"Qasim on Religion: Piety, night worship, pure heart are best","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Khatib reported: Qasim al-Ju'i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe religion is based upon cautious piety. The bes